                <span class="fs-5 text-dark fst-italic">Fastest Delivery</span>
                <p class="py-2">We Promise Deliver Order within 30 min</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-1 p-3">
                <span><i class="fa-solid fa-envelopes-bulk text-success mx-2 fs-4"></i></span>
                <span class="fs-5 text-dark fst-italic">Easy Order</span>
                <p class="py-2">Get contactless delivery for restaurant takeout, groceries and more!</p>
            </div>


